---
title: Shrimp & Edamame Stir-Fry With Gochujang Aioli plus Rice, Zucchini & Sesame Seeds
description: This hearty stir-fry comes together fast for a fresh and filling meal that's loaded with colorful veggies. You'll sizzle up zucchini, edamame, cabbage, and carrots in soy-chili sauce, then serve over a bed of fluffy rice. Drizzle savory-spicy-sweet gochujang mayo atop, and finish with a sprinkle of scallion greens for a zippy finale.
